checkers.util

Class GraphQualifierHierarchy

  • @Nullable java.lang.Object
    • @Nullable checkers.types.QualifierHierarchy
      • checkers.util.MultiGraphQualifierHierarchy
        • checkers.util.GraphQualifierHierarchy

  • public class GraphQualifierHierarchy
extends MultiGraphQualifierHierarchy
    Represents the type qualifier hierarchy of a type system. This class is immutable and can be only created through GraphQualifierHierarchy.GraphFactory.
